<plot>An aging silent film actress hires a private eye and his wacky but helpful assistant to track down her missing daughter, Bellflower. The two follow a succession of bizarre, obscure clues, until they track down the location of the kidnappers and the daughter. There turn out to be several catches, though - the girl is not her daughter, and things are generally not at all what they seem to be.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?668126</url></doc>
